snippet: LEAD: A strong aftershock to Wednesday's earthquake was felt in a wide area of Southern California today. The earthquake caused a rockslide on a mountain road, but there were no reports of significant damage or injuries....
lead_paragraph: LEAD: A strong aftershock to Wednesday's earthquake was felt in a wide area of Southern California today. The earthquake caused a rockslide on a mountain road, but there were no reports of significant damage or injuries.
